# Bill of Materials (BOM)

Complete component list for the RC Ornithopter Flight Stabilization System.

## Electronics

| # | Component | Model / Part | Quantity | Key Specs |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Microcontroller | Arduino Nano | 1 | ATmega328P, 16MHz, 5V |
| 2 | IMU Sensor | MPU6050 Breakout | 1 | 6-axis, I2C, 3.3V/5V |
| 3 | BLDC Motor | F23700 3500KV | 1 | Composite, high RPM |
| 4 | ESC | 30A ESC | 1 | 2–3S LiPo, BEC 5V/3A |
| 5 | Servo Motor | SG90 | 2 | 9g, 1.8kgf·cm |
| 6 | RC Transmitter | FlySky FS-i6 | 1 | 6CH, 2.4GHz AFHDS 2A |
| 7 | RC Receiver | FlySky FS-iA6 | 1 | 6CH, 2.4GHz |
| 8 | LiPo Battery (Drone) | 2S 7.4V / 3S 11.1V | 1 | Lightweight, 45min |
| 9 | Battery (RC Controller) | AA 1.5V Dry Cell | 4 | For FS-i6 transmitter |
| 10 | FPV Camera | WiFi Mini Cam | 1 | 640×480, 2.4G WiFi, 8g |
| 11 | JST-XH Connectors | JST-XH 2/3/4 Pin | 1 set | Battery + signal |

## Mechanical Structure

| # | Component | Material | Quantity | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 12 | Frame / Gearbox housing | Fiberglass sheet | As needed | Rigid, lightweight frame |
| 13 | Plastic Gears | POM/Nylon | 3 | Pinion A, Spur+Pinion B+C, Driven D |
| 14 | Wing Membrane | Polyethylene cover | 1 | Lightweight aerofoil surface |
| 15 | Wing Spars / Rods | Plastic / Carbon | 4 | Wing skeleton structure |
| 16 | Small Bearings | Steel ball bearing | 2–4 | Smooth gear rotation |
| 17 | Double Ball Joints | Steel | 4 | Wing lever linkages |
| 18 | Small Nuts & Bolts | M2 / M3 Steel | 1 set | Structural fastening |
| 19 | Foam Tape | EVA foam | 1 roll | Anti-vibration IMU mount |

## Tools Required

- Soldering iron + solder
- Hot glue gun
- Small screwdrivers (Phillips + flat)
- Wire stripper
- Multimeter
- Arduino IDE (software)
- USB-A to Mini-USB cable (Arduino programming)

## Total Estimated Weight

| Component | Weight (g) |
|---|---|
| BLDC Motor | 12 |
| RC Receiver | 6.4 |
| Servo Motor (×2) | 9.8 × 2 = 19.6 |
| Battery | 30 |
| ESC Controller | 25 |
| Frame + Mechanical | 15 |
| Arduino + MPU6050 | ~8 |
| **Total** | **~116 g** |
